                        - <i class="hgi-stroke hgi-hard-drive"></i> [Start TimeMachine backup when a backup disk is connected](https://crank.lowtechguys.com/rule/YnZ4bsQAAACmAAAA4AR7IjIwIjoiZGVib3VuY2UiLCIyMQAQwAs1LjCGNDPgCXRtdXRpbCBzdGFydGJhY2t1cCAtLWF1dG8ILAAg53ZvbHVtZU0AP8AUdGVkSDUxUClCAA4IDetzaGVsbFNjcmlwdAggMDQADUZ2SBUxSEswSGRTwE8gVGnnYWNoaW5lICBx73doZW4gY29ubmVjdGluZygX52RyaXZlIn0GAAAAAAAAAGJ2eCQ)
