                        ---
                        ## How it works

                        Crank registers native listeners for macOS system events using CoreBluetooth, IOBluetooth, FSEvents, IOKit, and others. When an event fires and its conditions match, the action runs.

                        Shell scripts execute via `/bin/zsh` with your `.zshrc` sourced automatically, so your PATH, aliases, and functions are available.

                        All processing is done locally on your machine. No data is sent to any servers unless you explicitly enable Gemini or ChatGPT integration in settings.

        footer.flex.items-center.justify-between.px-2.md:px-8.max-w-[100vw].w-[100vw].h-24.text-gray-500.justify-self-end.mt-auto
            h4.font-extralight.text-gray-500.hidden.md:block The low-tech guys © 2026
            .links.w-full.md:w-auto
                / a.text-red-hot.ml-4 href="/contact" Contact
        -stylus
            @import "stylus/base"

            #app-icon
                filter: drop-shadow(0 0px 1px rgba(120, 80, 10, 0.4)) drop-shadow(0 9px 17px rgba(120, 80, 10, 0.4))

            blockquote
                background-color alpha(black, 0.05)
                color black
                padding 0.5rem
                border-radius 0.5rem
                margin 1rem 0
                font-size 0.85rem
                font-style italic
                font-weight 300
                line-height 1.5
                > *:first-child
                    margin-top 0
                > *:last-child
                    margin-bottom 0
                > *:only-child
                    margin 0
                em
                    color var(--color-mauve-gray)
            em, strong
                color var(--color-mauve-gray)
            h1, h2
                color var(--color-mauve-lightgray)
            h3
                color var(--color-mauve-gray)
            a
                color var(--color-mauve-pink)
                text-decoration-style dashed
            code
                font-size smaller
            code, .code
                font-family monoSpace
                font-weight 600
                color var(--color-rose-900)
                background var(--color-rose-50)
            pre
                margin 1rem 0
                code
                    color var(--color-rose-100)
                    font-size 0.8rem
            .links
                a
                    background-color alpha(black, 0.1)
                    color black

        -coffee
            if window.location.hash.includes('buy')
                window.location.href = 'https://crank.subsol.one'

            setTimeout =>
                vid = document.getElementById('crank-hero-video')
                img = document.getElementById('crank-hero-img')
                vid.classList.remove('opacity-0')
                vid.classList.add('opacity-100')
                setTimeout =>
                    vid.play()
                , 1000

            , 3000
